"cli.help" = "ShengJi CLI\n\nUsage:\n  LocalScribe --cli models [--json]\n  LocalScribe --cli download <model-id>\n  LocalScribe --cli remove <model-id>\n  LocalScribe --cli transcribe <audio-or-video> [--engine whisper|sensevoice|parakeet] [--model <model-id>] [--compute auto|coreml|metal|cpu] [--language en_US] [--translate-to zh-Hans] [--translation-provider apple|nllb] [--format txt|md|json|pdf|srt|vtt] [--output <path>]\n  LocalScribe --cli translate <text> --source en_US --target zh-Hans [--provider apple|nllb]\n\nCommon model IDs:\n  whisper.largeV3TurboQ5\n  whisper.largeV3Turbo\n  sensevoice.int8_2025\n  parakeet.tdt06bV3Int8\n\nNotes:\n  CLI file transcription supports Whisper, SenseVoice, and NVIDIA Parakeet.\n  The backend is selected automatically by default and the resolved path is reported on stderr. Standard Whisper Metal models do not use ANE automatically.\n  Translation supports Apple Translation and NLLB. Headless Apple Translation CLI sessions require macOS 26; NLLB is available on macOS 15.5+.";
